0 -14 Td ([ -api-key file ]) Tj
0 -14 Td ([ -supervisor path ]) Tj
0 -14 Td ([ -debug-pprof ]) Tj
0 -14 Td (DESCRIPTION) Tj
0 -14 Td (**BreathGSLB**) Tj
0 -14 Td (is a compact authoritative server that selects A and AAAA answers based on) Tj
0 -14 Td (live health checks.  It serves normal DNS records while optionally) Tj
0 -14 Td (synthesising AAAA from A via DNS64.  The daemon listens on UDP and TCP for) Tj
ET
endstream endobj
